{{Quote|The suit's adapted for pressurized hydrogen sulphide. Smells like death died and got left in the sun.|Chelli Aphra, on Hallio Bas' pressure suit|<ref name="Doctor Aphra (2016) 15">[[Doctor Aphra (2016) 15|''Doctor Aphra'' (2016) 15]]</ref>}}
[[File:Tambor_Covetous.png|thumb|right|200px|The Skakoan [[Wat Tambor]] wearing a pressure suit]]
'''Pressure suits''' were worn by members of the [[Skakoan]] [[species]] to survive off of their [[homeworld]] of [[Skako]], a [[planet]] whose [[atmosphere]] and pressure was extremely different from the [[The galaxy|galactic]] standard.<ref name="Ultimate Star Wars">''[[Ultimate Star Wars]]''</ref> Without one such suit, the body of a Skakoan would explode in a standard, [[oxygen]]-based [[atmosphere]].<ref name="Updated and Expanded">''[[Star Wars Character Encyclopedia: Updated and Expanded]]''</ref>

